title: Blood Money - Radio Drama
description:
1 x 60 mins

A thriller with an unusual twist at the end, by the always reliable R D Wingfield.

On his his day as his job as the new manager of a small branch of Berrington's Bank, the manager receives a 'phone call - his daughter has been kidnapped and he must steal a large amount of money from his new branch. Further instructions, but these become more bizarre as the play continues until its unexpected denouement
